name: KING & QUEEN
description:
Insights from the Dreaming Pool - The mythic story of who you are and how you relate and move in the world this way.

Power, majesty, royalty, twin flames, support, role models, recognising the majesty in each other, respecting it brings it out in the other. The royalty of the soul. Seeing yourself reflected in another. Responsibility to be who you are. You can’t hide when you see yourself in another. 

Accept your magnificence, it is supported by your reflection. 

When you acknowledge your own wings and then release them you will be ready for your King or your Queen. A King wants a Queen and a Queen wants a King. They wont settle for anything less. Don’t be afraid, you’ll be a unit supporting each other. Leaders, leading their people, inspiring and ruling with a just fair hand, philosopher Kings and Queens. 

The Dreaming Pool Oracle is a collaboration between artists Maia Mellier 🕸 🕷 (@maiamellier) & AEVIN (@aevin_io)
